Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Chinese state visit
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bx2w
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 4 Feb 1979
Carter welcomes Deputy Premier Deng on first Chinese state visit to US for 30 years. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.